# GitHub / git ops

When the user is unsure about GitHub, PRs, Dependabot, branch protection, force-push, collaborators, or pushes to `main`, load and follow [`ai/skills/github-maintainer/SKILL.md`](../../ai/skills/github-maintainer/SKILL.md) (Cursor mirror: `.cursor/skills/github-maintainer/SKILL.md`).

Decide safely. Do not dump option menus. Never merge conflicted PRs. Default flow: branch → PR → `validate` green → squash merge.
